VerbTeX Network Protocol (VNP)
------------------------------
A document-first protocol for human–AI collaboration.

VNP defines a simple, auditable header embedded in LaTeX/PDF documents
to support routing, integrity verification, and archival synchronization.

Repository Structure:
- protocol/spec.txt                         (main specification)
- protocol/VNP_Packet_Template_v0.1.txt     (ready-to-copy header)
- protocol/schema.json                      (machine-readable format)
- protocol/examples/example_packet_v0.1.txt (reference packet)
- protocol/VERSION.txt                      (version record)
